title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your current acute sensitivity to the sights, smells, and sounds around you elicits strong emotional responses from you. Choose to create and enjoy the ambience that is the most pleasing to you. Take active steps to avoid commotions and environments that trouble you today. Be mindful that no one else is responsible for arranging your setting to your liking except you. You are your own best caretaker. Happily, you might find that others are calmed by the soothing scene you manifest and may wish to plug into your world. A joy shared is a joy doubled. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
